ygData.msgSnippet: Salutations Ginette! I know this is an old post, but is it too late to say hi. ... I play a bunch of characters but the are all on the Xygony server. Mostly
ygData.messageBody:
Salutations Ginette!

I know this is an old post, but is it too late to say
hi.
:o)
I play a bunch of characters but the are all on the
Xygony server. Mostly lately I've been playing . . .

Venerable Melwen Shadowbow lvl 65 High Elf Cleric of
Tunare
Linnathon Serkeore lvl 47 Dark Elf Agnostic
Enchantress
Chansonette lvl 22 Vah Shir Agnostic Bard (this is my
baby kitty)
:o)

There are more but I wont list them all, and I do have
a lvl 3 or 4 bard on Kazic Thule but as its actually
my oldest toon you can see I don't play her much.

Anyway it's nice to see you hear and if there is ever
anything I can do please let me know.

:o)
Buttercup
